pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: p-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 50, 1100, 45]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>B2B Procurement Is Broken at Every Step</p>

  - elementId: p-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 105, 80, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 2
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card1
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 140, 360, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: p-icon1
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 160, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:comment-dots"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 200, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$ink"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>RFQs Are Lost in WhatsApp</strong></p>

  - elementId: p-card1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 240, 320, 100]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Buyers send quotes via email and chat. No tracking, no audit trail, no history. The same conversation happens 5 times.</p>

  - elementId: p-card2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [460, 140, 360, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: p-icon2
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [480, 160, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:file-excel"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 200, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$ink"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Tracking Lives in Spreadsheets</strong></p>

  - elementId: p-card2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 240, 320, 100]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Order status is a phone call away. Procurement teams maintain 5+ spreadsheets that never sync. Errors are inevitable.</p>

  - elementId: p-card3
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [860, 140, 360, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: p-icon3
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [880, 160, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:money-bill-wave"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 200, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$ink"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Payments Are Reconciled Blindly</strong></p>

  - elementId: p-card3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 240, 320, 100]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>"Did you pay?" / "I didn't receive it." Bank transfers with no shared record. Disputes take weeks to resolve.</p>

  - elementId: p-card4
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 390, 360, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: p-icon4
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 410, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:box-open"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 450, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$ink"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Assets Disappear After Delivery</strong></p>

  - elementId: p-card4-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 490, 320, 100]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Procured items are forgotten in warehouses. No one knows what the company owns, where it is, or what condition it's in.</p>

  - elementId: p-card5
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [460, 390, 360, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: p-icon5
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [480, 410, 28, 28]
    iconName: "fas:star-half-stroke"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$copper"

  - elementId: p-card5-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 450, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$ink"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Trust Is Word-of-Mouth</strong></p>

  - elementId: p-card5-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 490, 320, 100]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Vendor reliability is based on who someone knows. No verified reviews, no transaction history, no accountability.</p>

  - elementId: p-big-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [860, 420, 360, 70]
    content:
      style: "$bigNumber"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>30%+</p>

  - elementId: p-big-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [860, 500, 360, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$slate"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [center, top]
      text: |
        <p>of procurement time is spent on coordination, not purchasing</p>

  - elementId: p-pagenum
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1160, 670, 60, 30]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>04</p>